We thought we'd help do the sums. If you cleared the debt in
35 mths, you'd be £4,610 up from the switch.

Current or former EE or T-Mobile customers - are you due a
share of £1m refund? ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/news/phones/2015/01/ee-refunds-1m-after-mistakenly-charging-vat-on-non-eu-data ) Many were wrongly charged VAT for data roaming outside Europe
and are due £2-£80 refunds. Check if you're owed. EE refunds ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/news/phones/2015/01/ee-refunds-1m-after-mistakenly-charging-vat-on-non-eu-data )

£5 Asos dresses, £19 Kurt Geiger shoes, £20 Converse. ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/deals/bargains-deals-discounts#jansales )Jan sales now boosted. Limited stock, sale bargains. ( http://www.moneysavingexpert.com/deals/bargains-deals-discounts#jansales )


