<a name="energy" id="energy" style="color: #0047d9;"></a><a href="http://www.msetool.co.uk/redirect/energy_toppicks" class="headline" style="color: #0047d9; font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 20px; text-decoration: none;">Don't fall for British Gas &amp; Scot Power's 5  <span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #222; font-weight: bold;">These trivial price cuts risk giving many  false confidence they're on a good deal. They're not. Don't be fooled </span></a>
